1. Which product generates the most revenue?
SELECT product, ROUND(SUM(totalprice)) AS revenue
FROM dataset
GROUP BY product
ORDER BY revenue DESC
LIMIT 1;

2. What is the average order value per payment method?
Query
SELECT PaymentMethod, SUM(totalprice) / COUNT(OrderID) AS AOV
FROM dataset
GROUP BY PaymentMethod
ORDER BY AOV;

3. How many orders were cancelled vs delivered vs returned?
Query
SELECT OrderStatus, COUNT(OrderID) AS orders
FROM dataset
WHERE OrderStatus IN ('Cancelled', 'Delivered', 'Returned')
GROUP BY OrderStatus
ORDER BY orders;

4. Which referral source brings in the highest spending customers?
Query:
SELECT ReferralSource, SUM(TotalPrice) AS AmountSpend
FROM dataset
GROUP BY ReferralSource
ORDER BY AmountSpend;

